{"word":"G5049 - τελείως - teleíōs - tel-i'-oce - To the end","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τελείως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">teleíōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tel-i'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">To the end</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பூரணமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"perfectly, completely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G5046 - τέλειος - téleios - tel'-i-os/5046\">G5046</a>; <i>completely</i>, that is, (of hope) <i>without wavering:</i> - to the end.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2005/2005\">G2005</a>, <a href=\"#/G3838/3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930/4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931/4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046/5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047/5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048/5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049/5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050/5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051/5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5052/5052\">G5052</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055/5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056/5056\">G5056</a>"}]}